                                            </div>
                                            <p class="mb-2">• Personal details can be updated</p>
                                            <p class="mb-2">• Service categories cannot be changed</p>
                                            <p class="mb-2">• Status can be activated/deactivated</p>
                                            <p class="mb-0">• Changes are logged for audit</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                </div>
            </div>
